Every business needs a legal foundation. Jordan Flake works with Henderson and Las Vegas entrepreneurs, small business owners, and growing companies to build that foundation — from the entity formation documents to the contracts that govern daily operations.

We believe in practical legal counsel. Not every business issue needs a lawsuit — sometimes it needs a well-drafted contract, a clear operating agreement, or a strategic conversation about risk. When disputes do arise, we have the litigation capability to protect your interests.
